Sentencas: This paper proposes a recent approach-based moth-flame optimizer (MFO) to enhance the output power of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) via identifying the optimal parameters of its model.
Titulo: Recent moth-flame optimizer for enhanced solid oxide fuel cell output power via optimal parameters extraction process

Sentencas: The cell is modeled via artificial neural network (ANN) trained by experimental dataset.
Titulo: Recent moth-flame optimizer for enhanced solid oxide fuel cell output power via optimal parameters extraction process

Sentencas: Six inputs are fed to ANN to get the SOFC terminal voltage.
Titulo: Recent moth-flame optimizer for enhanced solid oxide fuel cell output power via optimal parameters extraction process

Sentencas: Levenberg-Marquardt is used in training process with minimizing the mean squared error (MSE).
Titulo: Recent moth-flame optimizer for enhanced solid oxide fuel cell output power via optimal parameters extraction process

Sentencas: The SOFC model polarization curves are compared to experimental data under variable operating conditions.
Titulo: Recent moth-flame optimizer for enhanced solid oxide fuel cell output power via optimal parameters extraction process

Sentencas: The proposed MFO is employed to estimate the optimal values of SOFC model, anode support layer (ASL) thickness; ASL porosity; thickness of electrolyte and cathode functional layer (CFL) thickness to enhance the SOFC extracted power.
Titulo: Recent moth-flame optimizer for enhanced solid oxide fuel cell output power via optimal parameters extraction process

Sentencas: Furthermore, a quantitative and qualitative comparative study with ANN-based SOFC optimized via Genetic Algorithm (GA), Social Spider Optimizer (SSO), Radial Movement Optimizer (RMO) and the experimental data is presented under different operating conditions.
Titulo: Recent moth-flame optimizer for enhanced solid oxide fuel cell output power via optimal parameters extraction process

Sentencas: Sensitivity analysis is performed by changing the upper and lower thresholds of the estimated variables.
Titulo: Recent moth-flame optimizer for enhanced solid oxide fuel cell output power via optimal parameters extraction process

Sentencas: The proposed ANN-MFO approach enhanced the SOFC power by 18.92% and 5.56% in comparison with ANN-GA and ANN-RMO respectively.
Titulo: Recent moth-flame optimizer for enhanced solid oxide fuel cell output power via optimal parameters extraction process

Sentencas: The obtained results confirmed the significance of the proposed MFO in enhancing of the SOFC output power.
Titulo: Recent moth-flame optimizer for enhanced solid oxide fuel cell output power via optimal parameters extraction process
